`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`
**Why this was already complete:** The production run (noted in MEMORY.md) built 7,594 tests across 256 suites. US-008's compression system was implemented during that sweep — the `systems-engineer` agent handled core game loop systems including compression.

**Design pattern worth noting:** The compression system separates *logic* (`compression.ts` — timer, powder deduction, cube creation) from *juice* (`compressionJuice.ts` — screen shake, pressure gauge, heat overlay). This is a clean separation that keeps the core system fully testable in Node.js without any Three.js/R3F dependencies.
